snippet.title: CABAL: Return of Action Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
A millennium has passed in relative peace for the denizens of Nevareth, but an ancient evil has stirred, throwing the world into chaos that heroes must rise to meet. Playing as one of 8 powerful classes, it’ll be up to players to quell the forces looking to annihilate everything in their path. 

Your Legacy Awaits! 

To find our more about us, check us out on our Socials Below!
